---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — CTRL+WATCH Magazine"
  description="CTRL+WATCH is a retro gaming magazine reviewing YouTube channels. Read our manifesto, scoring system, and meet Yob."
>
  <article class="about">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- HEADER -->
      <header class="about-header">
        <h1 class="about-title">ABOUT CTRL+WATCH</h1>
      </header>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <!-- MANIFESTO -->
      <section class="manifesto-section">
        <div class="manifesto-text">
          <p>There was a time when someone else decided what you watched.
          Three networks. A handful of music channels. If you were lucky,
          a magazine told you what was worth your time — and you trusted it,
          because the people writing it cared more about the thing than
          the business of the thing.</p>

          <p>YouTube killed the gatekeeper and replaced it with an algorithm.
          And the algorithm doesn't care if something is good.
          It cares if something is sticky.</p>

          <p>CTRL+WATCH exists because we think YouTube deserves what gaming
          had in the 80s and 90s: a magazine that is loud, opinionated,
          and unafraid to put a number on things. A magazine that will tell
          you Dan Carlin's Hardcore History is a 96/100 and explain exactly why.
          A magazine that will find the channel with 3,000 subscribers that's
          making better content than creators with 30 million.</p>

          <p class="manifesto-tagline">Your algorithm is broken. We're the fix.</p>

          <p>Welcome to CTRL+WATCH. Press start.</p>

          <p class="manifesto-attribution">— The Editor</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <!-- HOW WE SCORE -->
      <section class="scoring-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">HOW WE SCORE</h2>
        <p class="scoring-intro">Every channel reviewed in CTRL+WATCH receives a score from 0 to 100. Here's what the numbers mean:</p>

        <div class="score-table-wrapper">
          <table class="score-table" role="table" aria-label="Scoring system">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th scope="col">RANGE</th>
                <th scope="col">VERDICT</th>
                <th scope="col">WHAT IT MEANS</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td><span class="score-range score-legendary">90–100</span></td>
                <td class="score-verdict">LEGENDARY</td>
                <td>Essential viewing. Drop everything.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><span class="score-range score-excellent">75–89</span></td>
                <td class="score-verdict">EXCELLENT</td>
                <td>A must-subscribe. Serious craft on display.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><span class="score-range score-good">60–74</span></td>
                <td class="score-verdict">GOOD</td>
                <td>Worth your time. Real signal in the noise.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><span class="score-range score-average">45–59</span></td>
                <td class="score-verdict">AVERAGE</td>
                <td>Has moments. Algorithm food with flashes of quality.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><span class="score-range score-weak">25–44</span></td>
                <td class="score-verdict">WEAK</td>
                <td>Something's off. Watch at your own risk.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><span class="score-range score-skip">0–24</span></td>
                <td class="score-verdict">SKIP</td>
                <td>We watched it so you don't have to. You're welcome.</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p class="scoring-note">Scores are final. We don't re-score based on channel complaints. We may re-score based on genuine growth or decline.</p>
      </section>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <!-- MEET YOB -->
      <section class="yob-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">MEET YOB</h2>
        <div class="yob-content">
          <div class="yob-art-wrapper">
            <pre class="yob-art-large" aria-label="Yob mascot pixel art">
    ▄▄▄▄▄
  ██o   o██
  ██  ▄  ██
  ██  ▀  ██
   █▄▄▄▄▄█
    ▀▀ ▀▀</pre>
            <p class="yob-name">YOB v1.0</p>
          </div>
          <div class="yob-bio">
            <p>Yob was born inside a dead pixel on a phosphor monitor sometime in 1987. Nobody knows exactly when — the monitor's clock had been wrong since 1984.</p>
            <p>He spent his early years watching test patterns and crash screens, developing a deep appreciation for content that didn't waste his time. He migrated to CRT televisions in the early 90s, absorbing every issue of every gaming magazine he could find.</p>
            <p>When YouTube launched in 2005, Yob watched the entire platform in three days. His conclusion: most of it was noise. A small fraction was signal. Nobody was writing about the difference.</p>
            <p>So he founded CTRL+WATCH. He is the magazine's only full-time employee, mascot, and chief opinion officer. He does not take sponsorships. He does not have an algorithm. He has opinions.</p>
            <p class="yob-catchphrase">His catchphrase: "I've seen better pixels."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <!-- CTA -->
      <section class="about-cta">
        <a href="/issues/001/" class="btn">READ ISSUE #001 ▶</a>
      </section>

    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .about-header {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ===== MANIFESTO ===== */
  .manifesto-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .manifesto-text {
    max-width: 720px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .manifesto-text p {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.9;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .manifesto-tagline {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace !important;
    font-size: var(--text-md) !important;
    color: var(--green) !important;
    text-shadow: var(--glow-green);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em !important;
    line-height: 1.8 !important;
  }

  .manifesto-attribution {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace !important;
    font-size: var(--text-sm) !important;
    color: var(--text-secondary) !important;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em !important;
    padding-top: var(--space-sm);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* ===== SCORING ===== */
  .scoring-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--green);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .scoring-intro {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .score-table-wrapper {
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .score-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  }

  .score-table th {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 8px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-align: left;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .score-table td {
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .score-table tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .score-table tr:hover td {
    background: var(--bg-card);
  }

  .score-range {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    white-space: nowrap;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .score-legendary { color: var(--yellow); }
  .score-excellent { color: var(--green); }
  .score-good      { color: var(--cyan); }
  .score-average   { color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .score-weak      { color: var(--orange); }
  .score-skip      { color: var(--red); }

  .score-verdict {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-primary) !important;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .scoring-note {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--green);
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
  }

  /* ===== YOB SECTION ===== */
  .yob-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .yob-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .yob-art-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .yob-art-large {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--green);
    text-shadow: var(--glow-green);
    line-height: 1.3;
    white-space: pre;
  }

  .yob-name {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 8px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .yob-bio {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .yob-bio p {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .yob-catchphrase {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace !important;
    font-size: var(--text-sm) !important;
    color: var(--green) !important;
    text-shadow: var(--glow-green);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em !important;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* ===== CTA ===== */
  .about-cta {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .yob-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .yob-art-wrapper {
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
